                    <Code Tag>PaginationItem</Code> the pagination item, which can be active or not.
                </Paragraph>
                <UnorderedList>
                    <UnorderedListItem>
                        <Paragraph>
                            <Code Tag>PaginationLink</Code> the link to the destination page, which will trigger the <Code Tag>Clicked</Code> event.
